This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with visual tracking. It may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories as it proposes a novel algorithm that addresses appearance changes over time. Additionally, it may belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) and Robotics (cs.RO) categories as visual tracking is a crucial component in these fields.
